      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, presenting exactly as it did the day it left the showroom. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like finish and no stone chips, scratches, or swirl marks. Inside, the leather remains supple and the cabin still retains that new-car scent, with every electronic feature functioning perfectly. It has been meticulously garage-kept and serviced exclusively at the dealership, with a full set of records included. For a buyer seeking a collector-grade example that requires zero compromise, this is the perfect choice.",
