      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and is a dependable choice for anyone needing a solid daily driver. Mechanically, the engine and transmission are in good working order, though the car shows its age aesthetically. You will find several scratches and minor dings on the exterior panels, and the interior upholstery has some visible staining and wear. It has been regularly serviced, making it a functional and honest vehicle for its price point.",
