    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Hey there! Thanks for stopping by. You\u2019re looking at my absolute pride and joy. I\u2019ve babied this beauty since day one, and honestly, it still feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. It\u2019s been kept tucked away in a climate-controlled garage, and the paint still has that deep, mirror-like shine that\u2019ll make your neighbors jealous. Every time I get behind the wheel, it puts a massive smile on my face, and I know it\u2019ll do the same for you. It\u2019s practically a time capsule\u2014crisp, clean, and ready for its next adventure. Come on over, let\u2019s grab a coffee and I\u2019ll show you why this is the one you\u2019ve been waiting for!",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 29
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Offering a meticulously sorted example of an iconic performance platform. This chassis has undergone comprehensive subframe reinforcement with a bespoke resin injection and plate kit to ensure maximum torsional rigidity under load. The high-revving power plant features a fully overhauled Vanos system with cryo-treated hub tabs and recent rod bearing replacement using ACL race bearings for total peace of mind. Compression and leak-down numbers are within 2% of factory spec, confirming optimal ring seal and valvetrain health. The suspension is dialed with corner-balanced coilovers featuring linear-rate springs for neutral turn-in and precise feedback. Finished in a depth-defying paint correction, this is a turnkey, concours-ready machine for the discerning driver who demands mechanical sympathy and peak performance.",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
